release.changelog: Updates improve the stability and reliability of the application. Thank you for choosing us.

beta.changelog: BETA - With this update, we are beginning to test the redesigned application menu. This new interface replaces both the classic and old interfaces. Pressing the back button on your remote will open a full-screen menu. For a quick return experience, the back button will be automatically selected. We look forward to all your feedback on the new design.
